    title: International Historical Statistics
    description: International Historical Statistics, originally published under the editorial leadership of Brian Mitchell since 1983, is a collection of datasets taken from many primary sources, including both official national and international abstracts dating back to 1750. The data is published in three volumes covering more than 5,000 pages. It is edited and published by Palgrave Macmillan.
